description:
The Ban on India's rice exports are disturbing the global market. This only adds to the already unstable food prices. We cannot sit around and wait for things to get better. The appropriate action is to grow your own food. Join us as we help others to be self sustained.

Contact Us @ gardenevangelist@gmail.com

Happy Planting!
